    "The rest of the sessions will present the findings followed by discussion, implications and conclusion.",
    "Recent research focusing on chatbot technology shows that it has been successfully applied in various fields (Okonkwo & Ade-Ibijola, 2021; Wollny et al., 2021).",
    "Chatbots utilize AI or deep learning-based models and implement feedback through text or voice interfaces (Winkler & Söllner, 2018).",
    "Chatbots used as tutors epitomize open-ended tutoring, a departure from the closed-end tutoring model, which predominantly focuses on arriving at correct solutions to specific problems (Alam, 2022 (Alam,, 2023)).",
    "Through sophisticated natural language processing and machine learning algorithms, these bots facilitate interactive dialogues with students, seeking to furnish personalized aid and resources aligned with specific learning objectives (Fauzi et al., 2023; Rasul et al., 2023)."
